# Don't ship local dev artefacts into the build context — they can override
# what each stage's `pnpm install` produced. The previous "build sometimes
# works" was buildkit cache + locally-matching pnpm hashes; once a
# `pnpm install` on the host re-resolves a different .pnpm hash directory,
# `COPY apps/web` overlays the deps-stage symlinks with broken targets and
# `nuxt` becomes unresolvable.

# Workspace dependencies — every stage that needs them runs its own install.
**/node_modules/

# Nuxt / Nitro build outputs — recreated by the builder stage.
**/.nuxt/
**/.output/
**/.nitro/

# Local env / docker / git noise — never relevant inside the image.
.env
.env.*
!.env.example
.git/
.github/
.idea/
.vscode/
*.log
.DS_Store
